      </SupplementalInformationDetail>
      <SupplementalInformationDetail>
        <FormAndLineReferenceDesc>FORM 990, PAGE 6, PART VI, LINE 19</FormAndLineReferenceDesc>
        <ExplanationTxt>THE ORGANIZATION MAKES AVAILABLE ITS GOVERNING DOCUMENTS,CONFLICT OF INTEREST POLICY AND FINANCIAL STATEMENTS UPON WRITTEN REQUEST AND THE FINANCIAL INFORMATION IS AVAILABLE ON THE FEDERAL AUDIT CLEARINNG HOUSE DATA BASE.</ExplanationTxt>
